               <msContents>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i1">
                     <rubric>Nomina sacra; a few lines on the incipit page of Text I-1 (alternating with black lines); incipit of Text I-2; names of the donor and the scribe; titles of books to be read; directives to the ministers in Text I-2; notes written in the upper margins; elements of the punctuation signs; elements of Ethiopic numerals.</rubric>
